INSERT INTO `locations` VALUES (1,'Cohive Green Office Park 9','https://cohive.space/','02150820840','Green Office Park Ground, 2nd Floor, Jl. Grand Boulevard, BSD Green Office Park, Tangerang, Banten','https://www.google.com/maps/place/CoHive+Green+Office+Park+9/@-6.3021731,106.648219,17z/data=!4m12!1m6!3m5!1s0x2e69fb2b1526c19f:0x46b127f5e0dcf997!2sCoHive+Green+Office+Park+9!8m2!3d-6.3021731!4d106.6504077!3m4!1s0x2e69fb2b1526c19f:0x46b127f5e0dcf997!8m2!3d-6.3021731!4d106.6504077','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3965.7070214371934!2d106.64821901401636!3d-6.30217309543886!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2e69fb2b1526c19f%3A0x46b127f5e0dcf997!2sCoHive%20Green%20Office%20Park%209!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578037471751!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','If you are looking for an affordable coworking event space & private office around Tangerang, consider CoHive Green Office Park 9 BSD City. Located next door to the home of an international consumer goods company, CoHive Green Office Park 9 is in the middle of BSD City new business district. \n\nIt\'s within walking distance from The Breeze, an outdoor lifestyle center which features Golds Gym, cinema XXI The Breeze, Farmer\'s Market, and various restaurants, to name a few: Chakra Lounge, Sushi Tei, and Bebek Bengil. \n\nIf you feel like networking and joining events in our nearby hub for coworking event space & private office, you might take a walk to CoHive The Breeze. \n\nHow to get there:\n\nGo straight on Jl. BSD Grand Boulevard. Right after passing Cisadane River, turn left. BSD Green Office Park is on your left.','2020-01-03 14:50:36','2020-01-03 14:50:36','cohive-green-office-park-9',''),(2,'centerflix','www.centerflix.com','0215701505','PT Carnegie- Universal Realty Management  Centerflix Boutique Office  Jl. Danau Toba 104, Pejompongan  Jakarta Pusat, 10210, Indonesia','https://www