 ecosystems in Indonesia especially in Fintech industry.\n\nStrategically located in Satrio Tower, Kuningan, FintechSPACE is targeted to officially commencing in June 2018. It is expected to be a platform for collaboration among stakeholders in the field of technology, including members of AFTECH, regulators, finance companies, venture capital firms, and startups.\n\nFintechSPACE will be the space for various activities, ranging in the form of seminars, workshop, and mentoring to support entrepreneurs and business owners. It can be a sphere for members to collaborate, exchange ideas and solutions, as a means to create new innovations, and become the center for network development to accelerate the growth of the Indonesian Fintech industry.','2020-01-06 15:15:07','2020-01-06 15:15:07','union-space','KOTA JAKARTA SELATAN'),(4,'Fj Bistro & Deli','www.google.com','0217182736','Jl. Kemang Raya No.25, RT.6/RW.1, Bangka, Kec. Mampang Prpt., Kota Jakarta Selatan, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12730','https://www.google.com/maps?q=Fj+Bistro+%26+Deli&rlz=1C1CHBD_idID862ID863&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjIhKTFyu7mAhW-H7cAHcj0B7oQ_AUoAnoECA8QBA','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3966.0294757759157!2d106.81348281476937!3d-6.259847695469001!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2e69f180ee8ad905%3A0x7fc9a416b3f81605!2sFj%20Bistro%20%26%20Deli!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578300300324!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Fj Bistro & Deli','2020-01-06 15:50:41','2020-01-06 15:50:41','fj-bistro-and-deli','KOTA JAKARTA SELATAN'),(5,'Werkspace','https://www.werkspace.id/','081290087480','SOHO CAPITAL Podomoro City, 19th Floor, Jl. Letjen. S. Parman Kav. 28, Tanjung Duren Selatan, Grogol Petamburan, Jakarta Barat 11470','https://www.google.com/maps?ll=-6.174579,106.789798&z=17&t=m&hl=en-US&gl=ID&mapclient=embed&cid=11684041957400176003','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3966.6725196359143!2d106.789798!3d-6.174579!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xa2260e416b98e583!2sWerkspace%20Soho%20Capital!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1578353327636!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Soho Capital\nThis beautiful location occupies the entire 19th Floor of Soho Capital\'s Premium Grade-A Office Tower, spread across a floor space of 1,500 m2. With sweeping views of the city skyline and direct access to West Jakarta\'s busiest commercial, office, shopping and residential \"Central Park Superblock\". It offers excellent cost to benefit ratio combined with unsurpassed convenience, which makes this location highly desirable for both local and multinational companies. Available services from coworking space, serviced office, virtual office, meeting rooms, conference rooms and event space. Demand is consistently high so whatever your office requirements, contact us today to ensure availability for you and your team. ','2020-01-07 06:31:26','2020-01-07 06:31:26','werkspace','KOTA JAKARTA BARAT'),(6,'Wellspaces Astra Lab','https://wellspaces.co/','08170052808','AstraLabs FIF TB Simatupang Jl. TB Simatupang Kav. 15, Menara FIF, 2nd Floor, RT.4/RW.1, Lb. Bulus, Cilandak, Jakarta Selatan, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12440','https://www.google.com/maps?ll=-6.291923,106.783711&z=15&t=m&hl=id&gl=ID&mapclient=embed&cid=15595196065963389077','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15863.141239852543!2d106.783711!3d-6.291923!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xd86d4431f2513095!2sAstra%20Labs%20Menara%20FIF%20TB%20Simatupang%20by%20wellspaces.co%20Coworking%20Space%20%26%20Serviced%20Office!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578353701501!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Nestled in FIF Tower, Astra Labs TB Simatupang offers a workspace that promotes innovation and productivity. Be it private office space, meeting rooms or virtual office needs, or event space that can cater up to 75 people, AstraLabs FIF TB Simatupang promises the ideal setup where business unlock their potentials and thrive to grow exponentially through our #WorkLearnNetwork environment that will shape start-ups and scale-ups to take off for future success.','2020-01-07 06:38:54','2020-01-07 06:38:54','wellspaces-astra-lab','KOTA JAKARTA SELATAN'),(7,'Wellspaces - Equity','https://wellspaces.co/','08170052808','wellspaces Equity Tower SCBD Equity Tower, 18th floor, RT.5/RW.3, Senayan, Kby. Baru, Kota Jakarta Selatan, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12190','https://www.google.com/maps?ll=-6.226263,106.808435&z=14&t=m&hl=en-US&gl=ID&mapclient=embed&cid=17883908927279139279','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d31730.270395345782!2d106.808435!3d-6.226263!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xf830686a95e909cf!2sWellspaces%20Equity%20Tower%20SCBD%20Coworking%20Space%20%26%20Serviced%20Office!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1578354155691!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','The coworking space occupies the 18th floor of the Equity Tower SCBD. So there’s plenty of light and views of the urban skyline. There are dozens of eateries nearby, and many locals enjoy cocktails on the sunny patio at Cork & Screw, Potatohead, Liberica Coffee, Lucy in the Sky, and the upcoming internationally acclaimed Hakassan are all within a few blocks. For an office that will impress clients in a neighborhood that means business, wellspaces Equity SCBD is the perfect location for your business. Near strategic areas such Senopati, Gunawarman, Senayan, Wijaya, Woltermonginsidi, Blok M, Sudirman, and more','2020-01-07 06:49:30','2020-01-07 06:49:30','wellspaces-equity','KOTA JAKARTA SELATAN'),(8,'GoWork - Senayan City','https://go-work.com','08119968896','Senayan City Panin Tower, 15th Floor, Senayan City Jl. Asia Afrika Lot. 19, Jakarta Pusat 10270','https://www.google.com/maps?ll=-6.226845,106.796683&z=16&t=m&hl=en-US&gl=ID&mapclient=embed&cid=5722224605227667003','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7932.558807529961!2d106.796683!3d-6.226845!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x4f696cf5f7984e3b!2sPanin%20Tower%2C%20Senayan%20City!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1578354701385!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','GoWork\nSENAYAN CITY\nWe chose Senayan City for its convenience and renowned location. Situated on Jalan Asia Afrika, not only is GoWork Senayan City part of an integrated complex comprising of high-end, seven-story shopping mall and office tower, but it is also minutes away from Plaza Senayan and Bina Nusantara University. This new workspace with a swoon-worthy view of the adjacent golf course is going to be a testament to our dedication to provide only the best of the best.','2020-01-07 07:01:49','2020-01-07 07:01:49','gowork-senayan-city','KOTA JAKARTA PUSAT'),(9,'Apiary - Kuningan','http://apiary.id','0818165222','Jl. Gatot Subroto No.Kav. 27, RW.3, Kuningan, Kuningan Tim., Setia Budi, Kuningan, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12950','https://www.google.com/maps?client=opera&q=Menara+Global,%0D%0AKuningan.&oe=UTF-8&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjK7Y_CmPDmAhWCYysKHY9xBJUQ_AUoAXoECBEQAw','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3966.2433311558507!2d106.81924301476917!3d-6.231619095489114!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2e69f3e3cebf84eb%3A0x77e38461f702ec5f!2sMenara%20Global!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578355537260!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Menara Global,\nKuningan.\nLocated in the bustling heart of Jakarta, Apiary is now offering coworking space in Kuningan.\nIf you are looking for an event space, meeting room, private office, shared desk or serviced office in Kuningan, South Jakarta, you are welcome to the hospitality of our community here in Apiary Coworking Space. Equipped with printer, free flow coffee, tea and other beverages, projector, sound system, locker space, daily events and more.','2020-01-07 07:10:34','2020-01-07 07:10:34','apiary-kuningan','KOTA JAKARTA PUSAT');
